ec0f84ea","type":"message","user":"U8CC7MDCL","text":"ですです","ts":"1602383098.036000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zBA"}]},{"client_msg_id":"242c03ef-00e2-4f8e-a784-80f80688d062","type":"message","user":"U8CC7MDCL","text":"not-internalなネットワークにも参加してるリバプロ置かないと無理ですね","ts":"1602383084.035600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Cs/N"}]},{"client_msg_id":"fcc054e4-193e-46ec-9742-3dc5842d9875","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"\u0026gt; ネットワークごと(複数コンテナ)ならゲートウェイになるコンテナを用意してネットワークを分離するのが楽そう\nこれとほぼいっしょだ。","ts":"1602382996.034000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"YPm"}]},{"client_msg_id":"3fb25571-a2a8-43a4-80ff-742d45f7c369","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あーリバプロってそういうことね。","ts":"1602382973.033100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"gX3b"}]},{"client_msg_id":"da2d539a-95f4-4871-b8b4-36790e569a97","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"`docker network create` に `--internal             Restrict external access to the network` ってあって、docker-compose もこれ使ってると思うんだけど、コレだとinboundのアクセスもできなくなっちゃわない?","ts":"1602382878.032600","edited":{"user":"U06BRP8VD","ts":"1602382904.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"NihZB"}]},{"client_msg_id":"996490a9-9a81-4b6f-88fc-2b86a44ba457","type":"message","user":"U8CC7MDCL","text":"internal network作れるのでdocker-composeでリバプロと組み合わせるとiptables触らなくても良いかもしれない。\nあとはコンテナ内でiptablesのルール書くならややこしいルール書かなくても済みそう。もしかしたらprivileged必要かもしれないけど。\n(そういやiptables再起動するとdockerのルール吹っ飛ぶのはもう直ったのかな)","ts":"1602382770.032000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"JyxNK"}]},{"client_msg_id":"3a25516c-4e8c-4b4b-bacf-5d1c86990ffb","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"僕が気になって調べた範囲をまとめると…\n\nコンテナ1つならiptablesを設定するのが楽そう。\nネットワークごと(複数コンテナ)ならゲートウェイになるコンテナを用意してネットワークを分離するのが楽そう。","ts":"1602382304.024500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"/7T"}]},{"client_msg_id":"c8d9e174-dc74-438f-960b-bd3af5794bb5","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"ネットワーク分けて、ルーティングするコンテナ作ってそこでやると実運用上は楽そうだな～","ts":"1602382127.023200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"Tu84"}]},{"client_msg_id":"56d5300a-121d-4396-bb86-b1d0270274d3","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"カスタム・ネットワーク・プラグインを使ってありそうな気もするけど。","ts":"1602381977.022600","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"IYG96"}]},{"client_msg_id":"8d2a011a-6759-4db1-8e41-7600d174fbf0","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"docker network でそういうネットワーク簡単に作れるかなとも思ったけどそうでもなさげ。","ts":"1602381910.022000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"zSuv"}]},{"client_msg_id":"2c4c3627-f9eb-4ca6-b203-bd7b3cc09a0d","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"iptables(firewall)以外の方法で、自発のoutboundだけを弾くってのは、逆に手間かかりそう。","ts":"1602381737.021300","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"0ZHy"}]},{"client_msg_id":"E37997F2-B33B-4B93-8BBF-D690B3618504","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"docker自体が内部でiptableを使ってネットワークの制御をしてるので","ts":"1602371184.020100","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"dKy"}]},{"client_msg_id":"7F150D64-AAC3-4D34-AD37-3A369F1EA3BC","type":"message","user":"UDDCM376D","text":"iptableしか方法がなさそう","ts":"1602371157.019200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"1Pc"}]},{"client_msg_id":"b36b212e-dd3c-4bb7-9a8f-0fbeff675b2a","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"もう寝るんですが、ちょっと質問を書き置きさせてください :bow:\nDocker のコンテナのネットワークなんですが、外部からのアクセスをポートで待ち受けるけど、コンテナ内から外部に対しての通信は禁止する、ってできますかね?\n調べると iptables でがんばるって話が出てきて、相当面倒そうだな、って印象なんですけど、もし何か方法知ってる方いたら教えていただけると助かります。わかりやすい資料への参照とかでも助かります :pray:","ts":"1602351853.018700","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"diF1l"}]}]
